{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}

This is a sub-template of {{tl|Succession box}}. It is used to check value of the {{para|before}} and {{para|after}} parameters, to see if they contains words which indicate that it would be better to use another template such as {{tl|S-new}}, {{tl|S-vac}} or {{tl|S-non}}, and to populate tracking categories.


